name: 'Chicken Pie' CD
description:
The second full length album from I Was Once a Dinosaur.

1. Welcome to Jurassic Park 
2. Constipated
3. Nudist Camp
4. I'm Not Gay (My Boyfriend Is)
5. Cousin' Lovin'
6. I Hate You (Please Die)
7. I Like Cheese
8. Monkey on the Loose
9. For The Dwarves
10. Worst Day of My Life
11. Gay You Up
12. I Wish I Were A Woman
13. Chopsticks
14. A Beautiful Love Song
15. Heartbroken
16. The Age of Man is Over (The Time of Acoustic Comedy has come)
bonus tracks 
17. The Scary Song
18. Drugs for Christmas

All songs written and performed by Matt Beauchamp & Isaac Crass.

Recorded and mixed by Tom Ralphs of Dying Breeds at Douchebag Cowboy Studio in Kenninghall, Norfolk.
